headline: Firing on All Cylinders: Fastly (NYSE:FSLY) Q1 Earnings Lead the Way
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how content delivery stocks fared in Q1, starting with Fastly (NYSE:FSLY).
